spec_data.Name: jets3t
spec_data.Description:
The JetS3t toolkit provides Java programmers with an API for interacting and
managing data stored in Amazon Simple Storage Service and Amazon CloudFront
content delivery network.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 07:14:33 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Java interface to Amazon S3 and CloudFront services
